subject: Re: [junit] Re: Asserting Equality Of Collection Elements
msgSnippet: The values from the map might include duplicate objects (the keys will not have any duplicates).  The HashSet, however, will not contain any duplicates. -shane
messageBody:
The values from the map might include duplicate objects (the keys will
not have any duplicates). The HashSet, however, will not contain any
duplicates.

-shane
